# Trap Word Immediate

D-Form

* twi TO,RA,SI

Pseudo-code:

    a <- EXTS((RA)[32:63])
    if (a < EXTS(SI)) & TO[0]  then TRAP
    if (a > EXTS(SI)) & TO[1]  then TRAP
    if (a = EXTS(SI)) & TO[2]  then TRAP
    if (a <u EXTS(SI)) & TO[3] then TRAP
    if (a >u EXTS(SI)) & TO[4] then TRAP

